description:
➤ Seventh-day Adventists: Facts and Fables - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/media/e/13502/t/seventh-day-adventists--facts-and-fables

Presidential candidate Ben Carson's religious faith is becoming a popular topic in the news and social media. Just what is a Seventh-day Adventist? What do they believe? Pastor Doug Batchelor explores this vital topic in this eye-opening presentation.
